#. Translators: A conversion direction shown in the settings panel.
msgid "Simplified Chinese → Traditional Chinese"
msgstr "簡體中文 → 正體中文"

#. Translators: A conversion direction shown in the settings panel.
msgid "Simplified Chinese → Traditional Chinese (Taiwan)"
msgstr "簡體中文 → 正體中文 (臺灣)"

#. Translators: A conversion direction shown in the settings panel.
msgid "Simplified Chinese → Traditional Chinese (Taiwan, with phrases)"
msgstr "簡體中文 → 正體中文 (臺灣，含詞彙轉換)"

#. Translators: A conversion direction shown in the settings panel.
msgid "Traditional Chinese → Simplified Chinese"
msgstr "正體中文 → 簡體中文"

#. Translators: A conversion direction shown in the settings panel.
msgid "Traditional Chinese (Taiwan) → Simplified Chinese"
msgstr "正體中文 (臺灣) → 簡體中文"

#. Translators: A conversion direction shown in the settings panel.
msgid "Traditional Chinese (Taiwan) → Simplified Chinese (with phrases)"
msgstr "正體中文 (臺灣) → 簡體中文 (含詞彙轉換)"

#. Translators: Title of the openccConverter category in NVDA's settings dialog.
#. Translators: Input gestures category for this add-on.
#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
msgid "OpenCC Chinese Converter"
msgstr "OpenCC 中文簡繁轉換"

#. Translators: Label for the conversion direction combo box in the settings panel.
msgid "Conversion &direction:"
msgstr "轉換方向(&D):"

#. Translators: Description of the command-layer gesture shown in Input Gestures.
msgid ""
"OpenCC Chinese Converter command layer. Then press s to convert the "
"selection, c to convert the clipboard, or w to swap the direction."
msgstr ""
"OpenCC 中文簡繁轉換指令層。接著按 s 轉換選取的文字、按 c 轉換剪貼簿,或按 w 交"
"換轉換方向。"

#. Translators: Description of the convert-selection command shown in Input Gestures.
msgid "Converts the selected text between Simplified and Traditional Chinese."
msgstr "在簡體與正體中文之間轉換選取的文字。"

#. Translators: Description of the convert-clipboard command shown in Input Gestures.
msgid "Converts the clipboard text between Simplified and Traditional Chinese."
msgstr "在簡體與正體中文之間轉換剪貼簿的文字。"

#. Translators: Description of the swap-direction command shown in Input Gestures.
msgid "Swaps the conversion direction."
msgstr "交換轉換方向。"

#. Translators: Reported when no text is selected.
msgid "No selection"
msgstr "沒有選取文字"

#. Translators: Reported when the clipboard contains no convertible text.
msgid "The clipboard is empty"
msgstr "剪貼簿是空的"

#. Translators: Reported when there is no text to convert.
msgid "There is no text to convert"
msgstr "沒有可轉換的文字"

#. Translators: Reported when conversion unexpectedly fails.
msgid "Conversion failed"
msgstr "轉換失敗"

#. Translators: Reported when a conversion is requested while one is still running.
msgid "Still converting, please wait"
msgstr "正在轉換中,請稍後"

#. Translators: Reported when the converted text could not be copied to the clipboard.
msgid "Could not copy the result to the clipboard"
msgstr "無法將結果複製到剪貼簿"

#. Translators: Announced after converting a large amount of text,
#. instead of speaking the whole result. {0} is the character count.
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Converted and copied {0} character to the clipboard"
msgid_plural "Converted and copied {0} characters to the clipboard"
msgstr[0] "已將 {0} 個字元轉換並複製到剪貼簿"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
msgid ""
"Offline Simplified/Traditional Chinese conversion.\n"
"Converts the selected text or the clipboard text between Simplified and\n"
"Traditional Chinese and speaks the result, which is also copied to the\n"
"clipboard. The conversion direction is configurable in the add-on settings "
"and\n"
"can be swapped on the fly. Everything runs fully offline using a bundled,\n"
"pure-Python OpenCC engine; no internet connection is required."
msgstr ""
"離線簡繁中文轉換。\n"
"在簡體與正體中文之間轉換選取的文字或剪貼簿的文字並朗讀結果,結果也會複製到剪貼"
"簿。\n"
"轉換方向可在元件設定中切換,也可以即時交換。\n"
"全部使用內建的純 Python OpenCC 引擎,完全離線運作,不需要網路連線。"

#. Brief changelog for this version
#. Translators: what's new content for the add-on version to be shown in the add-on store
msgid ""
"First release.\n"
"- Offline Simplified/Traditional Chinese conversion of the selected text or "
"the clipboard, fully offline.\n"
"- Press NVDA+shift+c, then s to convert the selection, c to convert the "
"clipboard, or w to swap the conversion direction.\n"
"- The conversion direction is configurable in the add-on settings."
msgstr ""
"首次發布。\n"
"- 在簡體與正體中文之間轉換選取的文字或剪貼簿的文字,完全離線。\n"
"- 按 NVDA+shift+c,接著按 s 轉換選取的文字、按 c 轉換剪貼簿,或按 w 交換轉換方"
"向。\n"
"- 轉換方向可在元件設定中切換。"
